    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/tupe-a-guide-to-the-2006-regulations"/>
    <title>TUPE - a guide to the 2006 regulations</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;The revised Transfer of Undertakings (Protection of Employment) Regulations came into force in 2006. These regulations provide rights to employees when their employer changes when a business is transferred to a new owner. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This publication provides guidance to employers, employees and their representatives to help them understand the regulations and comply with their legal requirements.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please note, this is general guidance; it should not be taken as a complete or authoritative statement of the law.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
