  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.bis.gov.uk/assets/biscore/employment-matters/docs/c/12-1215rf-consultation-on-implementing-employee-owner-status-form.doc"&gt;Consultation on implementing employee owner status: response form (DOC, 105 Kb) &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.bis.gov.uk/assets/biscore/employment-matters/docs/e/12-1228-equality-impact-implementing-employee-owner-status.pdf"&gt;Equality impact assessment of implementing employee owner status (PDF, 226 Kb) &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
